data.description: Here's your opportunity to enjoy living in a spacious 2-story beach house in the unique and eclectic seaside community of Flagler Beach. Located just a short block away from one of Florida's most distinctive beaches, with its 6 miles of uninterrupted dunes & cinnamon-hued coquina sand, this 3 bedroom/3 bath home prominently features a 12' wide by 22' long side porch where relaxing and rejuvenating at the day's beginning and the day's end are the norms. You'll love the home's generously-sized light-filled rooms, the kitchen with its abundance of cabinets and countertops, and the close proximity to all the activities that beach-living provides, including biking, hiking, swimming, fishing, and whatever else floats your boat! Plus there's a 2-Car Garage and a Laundry Room, windows that were replaced in 2020 and 2018, and a Roof and HVAC unit that were installed in 2016. Stop by and see this hidden gem, and start living the Florida lifestyle today!
